    "topic": "Example 1",
    "subtopics": [
      {
        "subtopic": "Table-based DI",
        "content": "**Table:**\n| Year | Sales (₹ lakh) |\n|------|----------------|\n| 2020 | 250            |\n| 2021 | 300            |\n| 2022 | 350            |\n\n**Q:** What is the percentage increase in sales from 2020 to 2022?\n**Solution:** (350−250)/250 × 100 = 100/250 × 100 = 40%\n**Answer:** 40%"
      }
